Package: broadlinkac
Version: 3.1-1
Depends: python3-light, python3-urllib, python3-json, python3-math, python3-threading, python3-datetime, python3-re, python3-socket, python3-ssl, python3-gzip, python3-broadlink, python3-schedule, python3-pip
Section: utils
Architecture: aarch64_generic
Maintainer: oywq00008-cell
License: MIT
Description: AI-powered smart AC controller for Broadlink RM series.
 Supports 17 AC brands, dual weather sources (Baidu/QWeather),
 NMC typhoon tracking, auto AC shutdown on storm <100km.
 v3.1: weather fallback chain, typhoon cache, log download, init guard,
  2h auto-adjust with storm intercept, LuCI dashboard polish.
 Installs: pip3 install hvac_ir after opkg install (see postinst).
